text: Mohammad Mohsin is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Khulna-2. ==Career== Mohsin was elected to parliament from Khulna-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mohammad Mohsin (politician)
